(1)       0 : =10                WSB_7E1_gc      =       001000B / 7 bits + Even Parity + 1 Stop Bits
(1)       0 : =14                WSB_7O1_gc      =       001100B / 7 bits + Odd Parity  + 1 Stop Bits
